\sum_{i=0}^{2n} (-3)^i
\sum_{i=0}^{n} (-3)^{2i} + \sum_{i=0}^{n - 1} (-3)^{2i +  1}
\sum_{i=0}^{2n} (-3)^i=\sum_{i=0}^{n} (-3)^{2i}+\sum_{i=0}^{n-1} (-3)^{2i+1}=\sum_{i=0}^{n} 3^{2i}-\sum_{i=0}^{n-1} 3^{2i+1}
-3 + 9 - 27 + 81 - 243 + 729 \mp \dots - 3^{2n-1} + 3^{2n}
(-3 + 9) + (-27 + 81) + (-243 + 729) \mp \dots + (-3^{2n-1} + 3^{2n})
6 + 54 + 486 + \dots + 6 * 3^{2n-2}
6(1 + 9 + 81 + \dots + 9^{n-1})
3^{2n-2} = 9^{n-1}
